roup non-top level variable declarations. My motivations are to increase alignment via `var` blocks, and to reduce mixing of adjacent `var` and `:=` declarations. We would require a minimum of 3 assignment lines before changing them to a `var` block.\r\n\r\nBefore\r\n```go\r\nfunc _() {\r\n\tvar a = 123\r\n\tvar banana = 456\r\n\tvar crabAppleAndCranberry = 789\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter\r\n```go\r\nfunc _() {\r\n\tvar (\r\n\t\ta                     = 123\r\n\t\tbanana                = 456\r\n\t\tcrabAppleAndCranberry = 789\r\n\t)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nBefore\r\n```go\r\nfunc _() {\r\n\tvar (\r\n\t\ta      = 123\r\n\t\tbanana = 456\r\n\t)\r\n\tcrabAppleAndCranberry := 789\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter\r\n```go\r\nfunc _() {\r\n\tvar (\r\n\t\ta                     = 123\r\n\t\tbanana                = 456\r\n\t\tcrabAppleAndCranberry = 789\r\n\t)\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nBefore\r\n```go\r\nfunc _() {\r\n\ta := 123\r\n\tbanana := 456\r\n\tcrabAppleAndCranberry := 789\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter\r\n```go\r\nfunc _() {\r\n\tvar (\r\n\t\ta                     = 123\r\n\t\tbanana                = 456\r\n\t\tcrabAppleAndCranberry = 789\r\n\t)\r\n}\r\n```","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mvdan/gofumpt/issues/80/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mvdan/gofumpt/issues/80/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":11661904132,"node_id":"REFE_lADOCqWoQc4cU4BCzwAAAAK3GokE","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mvdan/gofumpt/issues/events/11661904132","actor":{"login":"gavinelder","id":1226100,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyMjYxMDA=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1226100?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/gavinelder","html_url":"https://github.com/gavinelder","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gavinelder/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gav